OL,3,CPolice appeal after firework thrown
OL,4,Cinto McDonald's
OL,6,FA police investigation has begun after
OL,7,Fa firework was thrown into a branch of
OL,8,FMcDonald's in Bristol city centre in
OL,9,Fan "incredibly reckless" act.
OL,11,FThe incident happened in the Horsefair
OL,12,Fbranch of the fast-food restaurant, at
OL,13,Faround 8pm on 13 October 2025.
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset Police said the
OL,16,Fexplosive ricocheted off an order
OL,17,Fscreen and landed by a customer.
