OL,3,CPolice appeal after firework thrown
OL,4,Cinto McDonald's
OL,6,FSergeant Sean Underwood said no one
OL,7,Fwas injured, but the incident was
OL,8,F"incredibly reckless and shows
OL,9,Fcomplete disregard" for public safety.
OL,11,F"Fireworks can cause significant
OL,12,Finjuries, ranging from burns through
OL,13,Fto blindness, should they be handled
OL,14,Fincorrectly," he said.
OL,16,F'Incredibly reckless'
OL,18,FThe force has released a CCTV image of
OL,19,Fa man officers would like to speak to
OL,20,Fin connection with the incident.
