OL,3,CPolice appeal after firework thrown
OL,4,Cinto McDonald's
OL,6,FPolice believe the same person also
OL,7,Fkicked the door of the fast-food
OL,8,Frestaurant down the night before,
OL,9,Fsmashing a glass panel.
OL,11,FPolice said the man is believed to be
OL,12,Fbetween 16-18 years old. He is
OL,13,Fdescribed as between 5ft 10ins and 6ft
OL,14,Ftall, of slim build, with afro-style
OL,15,Fhair and a moustache.
OL,17,FCCTV shows him wearing a black
OL,18,FTrapstar coat, a hooded jacket, Nike
OL,19,Fjogging bottoms and black trainers. He
OL,20,Fis also shown carrying a black Nike
OL,21,Fbag.
