OL,6,FSergeant Underwood said that
OL,7,Fadditional patrols are being carried
OL,8,Fout in the area following the incident.
OL,10,F"Our Neighbourhood Policing Teams have
OL,11,Fbeen and will continue to carry out
OL,12,Fhigh-visibility patrols in the areas
OL,13,Fmost impacted and will be supported by
OL,14,Fcolleagues from specialist units,
OL,15,Fincluding our Mounted and dog
OL,16,Fsection," he said.
